9MjIxMDIwJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB05bef620=
" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D=
"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px=
; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-colo=
r: #ccc;">  causing dealers to hedge by buying a lot of the stock</a> and p=
ushing its price up to insane heights? Uh =E2=80=A6=C2=A0  maybe? That=E2=
=80=99s what they <em>said=C2=A0</em>they did, and the stock sure did go up=
, though the SEC=E2=80=99s report on the GameStop phenomenon <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29439806.290503/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cu=
