 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;">  mostly discounts</a> this =E2=80=9Cgamma squeeze=E2=80=9D s=
tory. <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29439806.290=
